  <title>Section 3: Relationships Between Quantitative Variables</title>

  <introduction>
    <p>In this section you will analyze data sets with two quantitative variables. The goal is to describe and model relationships between variables, beginning with graphical and numerical summaries and then moving to prediction with linear models.</p>
  </introduction>

